entry.title: IterateAI/OpenThreatDetection
entry.summary: Iterate.ai has open-sourced a powerful Weapons Detection AI software. The AI was trained on about 100 live guns, plus 20,000 videos of robberies and threats involving weapons. Our engineers taught the AI to detect guns, knives, kevlar vests, and robbery masks.
